title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update- Landing challenge - Bullseye landing
description:
In this video we will have a look at the latest FREE addon from Asobo/Microsoft which has been released which will add a landing challenge to MSFS. In this challenge you will need to land on a helipad. The heli pad which they selected is based on a recent Red Bull stunt pilot from Poland which landed on the helipad of the Burj Al Arab in Dubai. The helipad is located at the top of the hotel at 728 ft. above see level.
